  // For each app provide:
  //   name        - friendly name for the report
  //   appStoreId  - numeric ID from App Store URL (null if not on App Store)
  //   playStoreId - package name from Play Store URL (null if not on Play Store)
  //   logourl     - app's logo url from playstore for displaying in the report 
